# Note Taker
## License
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT) The application is covered under the [MIT License](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT).
## Description
My motivation for this project was to provide a valuable tool for small business owners to help them organize their thoughts and tasks, and ultimately increase their productivity and success. I built this project to address the needs of small business owners who require an efficient and user-friendly note-taking application to help them manage their work effectively, ultimately leading to increased productivity and success. This project solves the problem of disorganization and lack of productivity for small business owners by providing a reliable and user-friendly note-taking application to help them manage their thoughts and tasks effectively. Creating this application using Express.js allowed me to learn the benefits of using a robust web framework, including simplified routing and middleware management, which helped to streamline the development process and create a more efficient and scalable application.
