1. No installation required
2. Just go [https://still-lake-39330.herokuapp.com](https://still-lake-39330.herokuapp.com).


## Usage
Upon opening the note-taking application, you will be directed to a landing page that includes a link to access the note-taking functionality. Once on the notes page, the right-hand column enables you to input the title and text for a new note. Upon completion, a Save icon will be displayed at the top of the page. By clicking the Save icon, your newly created note will be saved and appear alongside previously existing notes in the left-hand column. To view an existing note, simply select it from the left-hand column, and it will appear in the right-hand column. If you wish to delete a previous note, click on the note from the left-hand column, and then select the Delete icon located in the navigation at the top of the page.

